Men's Room:  three urinals along left wall.  Two large stall toilets (wheelchair accessible) straight ahead from entrance.  Seat covers, sink, hand dryer in stall.  

Women's: six stalls.  Large, handicap accessible.  Each stall has own sink and hand dryers.  Accessible sinks and mirrors in centre of main bathroom area.
